1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:14,000
[SPEAKER_00] Dragi mladi, lijepo vas je vidjeti o velikom broju, malo podsjeća na ovo evanđelje, ova guža oko Isusa, jer su se bacali, kaže, na njega, da bi ga se dotakli.

2
00:00:14,000 --> 00:00:27,000
[SPEAKER_00] Mi smo još uvijek u ovome ciklusu predavanja od ljubavi. Puno puta čujem da vi mladi, kad je tema ljubavi, postavljate različita pitanja.

3
00:00:27,000 --> 00:00:34,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jedno od najdubljih pitanja koji mladi danas nose nije, šta vi mislite koje je to pitanje?

4
00:00:34,000 --> 00:00:46,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nije koga ću voljeti. Nažalost nije to. Nego je pitanje vrijedim li uopće da me neko voli.

5
00:00:46,000 --> 00:00:54,000
[SPEAKER_00] Bilo bi nekako normalno da si postavim u pitanje, da si vi postavite pitanje koga ću voljeti.

6
00:00:54,000 --> 00:01:04,000
[SPEAKER_00] Međutim, u razgovoru sa vama vidim da su nekima temelji vašeg identiteta poljuljani.

7
00:01:05,000 --> 00:01:18,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pa umjesto da si postavljate pitanje koga ću voljeti, mnogi mladi su došli do te razine da kažu vrijedim li uopće da me neko voli.

8
00:01:18,000 --> 00:01:27,000
[SPEAKER_00] Što se to vama dogodi da izgubite taj osjećaj identiteta i vrijednosti ko si?

9
00:01:29,000 --> 00:01:50,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ako si postavljamo takvo pitanje, a živimo u takvom vremenu gdje vaša vrijednost treba označavati različiti lajkovi, komentari, uspjesi, natjecanja i to je ono što vama serviraju društvene mreže.

10
00:01:50,000 --> 00:02:03,000
[SPEAKER_00] I zbog toga mnogi mladi gube svoj identitet i zato postavljaju ovakav pitanja, vrijedim li ja uopće? Hoće li mene uopće neko više voljeti?

11
00:02:03,000 --> 00:02:18,000
[SPEAKER_00] E, a zašto je to tako? Zato što u ovome svijetu u kojem vi pratite, u kojem vi živite, pogotovo ovaj svijet online, društvenih mreža, sve drugačije vrijednosti uči.

12
00:02:19,000 --> 00:02:34,719
[SPEAKER_00] Kako? Pa na primjer, ako si viđen, znači da postojiš. Ako te neko bira, znači da vrijediš. Ako si sam, postavlja se pitanje šta je s tobom?

13
00:02:34,719 --> 00:02:43,860
[SPEAKER_00] Ja mislim da vam je svima najmrže pitanje kaš se udat, kaš se o ženti. Ili zašto si sama, zašto si sam?

14
00:02:46,000 --> 00:02:53,900
[SPEAKER_00] Jer temelji vrijednosti su se poljuljali. Znači, samo ako sam viđen, primjećen, ja postojim.

15
00:02:53,900 --> 00:03:05,020
[SPEAKER_00] Samo, znači, ako me neko bira, saliječe, onda ja kao pod navodnicima nešto vrijedim, ali to nije to. To nije kršćanstje.

16
00:03:05,020 --> 00:03:13,400
[SPEAKER_00] Jer na kraju, ako gledamo na taj način, onda vrijediš oneliko koliko si poželjan.

17
00:03:14,659 --> 00:03:16,180
[SPEAKER_00] Jeste li svi poželjni?

18
00:03:16,180 --> 00:03:22,560
[SPEAKER_00] Niste u istim godinama, niste svi na isti način poželjni.

19
00:03:22,560 --> 00:03:26,060
[SPEAKER_00] Jel je to sve znači da niste više vrijedni?

20
00:03:26,060 --> 00:03:30,460
[SPEAKER_00] Pa niste pa šteta, ne ističe vam rok trajanja.

21
00:03:30,460 --> 00:03:36,860
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto su onda neki prihvatili da je za njih ljubavna priča završena

22
00:03:36,860 --> 00:03:41,360
[SPEAKER_00] i da njihova vrijednost više nije na cijeni.

23
00:03:41,360 --> 00:03:43,680
[SPEAKER_00] Di smo se pogubili?

24
00:03:43,680 --> 00:03:51,379
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, ako nisi u vezi, ako te niko ne želi, ako te niko ne bira,

25
00:03:52,379 --> 00:03:57,020
[SPEAKER_00] Ako te niko ne odabere, znači da i ne vrijediš.

26
00:03:57,020 --> 00:03:58,099
[SPEAKER_00] To nije istina.

27
00:03:58,099 --> 00:03:59,699
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto?

28
00:03:59,699 --> 00:04:02,520
[SPEAKER_00] Zato što to cijelamo glat malo biblijski.

29
00:04:02,520 --> 00:04:07,280
[SPEAKER_00] Da ne možemo naše života i našu vrijednost, naš identitet,

30
00:04:07,780 --> 00:04:12,479
[SPEAKER_00] mjeriti po društvenim mrežama, općem mijenju koje sada vlada,

31
00:04:12,479 --> 00:04:15,020
[SPEAKER_00] nego po onom što Bog kaže.

32
00:04:15,020 --> 00:04:21,040
[SPEAKER_00] Sjećate se onom, nedavno smo slavili krštenje Isuva.

33
00:04:21,040 --> 00:04:26,040
[SPEAKER_00] Kad Isus je bio kršten, a začuo se glas.

34
00:04:26,040 --> 00:04:28,920
[SPEAKER_00] Ovo je sin moj ljubljeni.

35
00:04:28,920 --> 00:04:36,920
[SPEAKER_00] Bog nije čekao da Isus nešto napravi, pa da kaže da on ljubljeni sin Boži.

36
00:04:37,560 --> 00:04:39,060
[SPEAKER_00] Bog nije postavio pitanje,

37
00:04:39,060 --> 00:04:42,399
[SPEAKER_00] bićeš moj ljubljeni sin ako uspiješ.

38
00:04:42,399 --> 00:04:47,019
[SPEAKER_00] Bićeš moj ljubljeni sin ako te ljudi prihvate.

39
00:04:47,019 --> 00:04:50,399
[SPEAKER_00] Bićeš moj ljubljeni sin ako uspiješ.

40
00:04:50,399 --> 00:04:54,100
[SPEAKER_00] Vidite, Bog to tako ne radi.

41
00:04:54,100 --> 00:04:59,199
[SPEAKER_00] Bog mu govori, tko je on prije nego što je išta učinio.

42
00:04:59,199 --> 00:05:03,139
[SPEAKER_00] Jer znamo da je to početak javnog djelovanja Isobog.

43
00:05:03,139 --> 00:05:07,279
[SPEAKER_00] I Boga voli iskreno, niti zbog uspjeha,

44
00:05:07,339 --> 00:05:11,040
[SPEAKER_00] niti zato što ga drugi primjećuju, niti zato što ga drugi prihvaćaju.

45
00:05:12,180 --> 00:05:16,579
[SPEAKER_00] Zato i vama, dragi mladi, vi niste vrijedni samo ako vas neko primjećuje,

46
00:05:16,579 --> 00:05:22,680
[SPEAKER_00] ako vas neko traži, ako vas neko hvali, ako ste uspješni.

47
00:05:22,680 --> 00:05:23,579
[SPEAKER_00] Niste.

48
00:05:23,579 --> 00:05:25,680
[SPEAKER_00] Jer onda to nema pravi identitet.

49
00:05:27,680 --> 00:05:47,220
[SPEAKER_00] Neko neko neko voli, to znači da sam ja vrijedan.

50
00:05:47,459 --> 00:05:51,319
[SPEAKER_00] Ako sam u vezi, opa, nešto ja i značim.

51
00:05:51,319 --> 00:05:55,579
[SPEAKER_00] Ako me netko izabere, pa ja imam neku vrijednost.

52
00:05:55,579 --> 00:06:02,060
[SPEAKER_00] Vjerujte mi, jako puno mladi tako razmislja o svojoj vrijednosti.

53
00:06:03,100 --> 00:06:07,759
[SPEAKER_00] A što ćemo, ako imamo ovako obrnuto razmišljanje o vrijednostima,

54
00:06:07,759 --> 00:06:11,639
[SPEAKER_00] što ćemo kad pukne veza?

55
00:06:11,639 --> 00:06:14,439
[SPEAKER_00] Što ćemo kad pukne brak?

56
00:06:15,439 --> 00:06:21,680
[SPEAKER_00] Ja svakodnevno se usrećem one koji su bili, imali ovakve temelje.

57
00:06:21,680 --> 00:06:28,839
[SPEAKER_00] I kad pukne veza ili brak, ne da pukne veza, već puca identitet.

58
00:06:28,839 --> 00:06:31,839
[SPEAKER_00] Puca u osobi vrijednost.

59
00:06:31,839 --> 00:06:35,600
[SPEAKER_00] I osoba ne samo što ostane zbog voljene osobe,

60
00:06:35,600 --> 00:06:38,459
[SPEAKER_00] nego ostane i bez dijela sebe.

61
00:06:39,519 --> 00:06:45,699
[SPEAKER_00] Zato što je svoj identitet, svoju vrijednost ravnala po nekoj drugoj osobi.

62
00:06:45,699 --> 00:06:51,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ili po tome što je bila ili voljena, ili tražena, ili primjećena.

63
00:06:51,000 --> 00:06:57,519
[SPEAKER_00] I ja vidim danas da mnogi tako i dožive.

64
00:06:57,519 --> 00:07:00,120
[SPEAKER_00] Ali zašto ovo govorim?

65
00:07:00,120 --> 00:07:02,379
[SPEAKER_00] Bog ima drugačiju logiku.

66
00:07:02,379 --> 00:07:04,699
[SPEAKER_00] Bog nas jednostavno ljubi.

67
00:07:04,699 --> 00:07:07,019
[SPEAKER_00] Ljubi nas svake kakve jesmo.

68
00:07:07,639 --> 00:07:13,139
[SPEAKER_00] Vjerujte mi da mnogi mladi traže, naravno da je lijepo biti zaljubljeni,

69
00:07:13,139 --> 00:07:14,480
[SPEAKER_00] da se ostvarite u tome.

70
00:07:14,480 --> 00:07:20,560
[SPEAKER_00] Ali druga osoba nikad ne može zamijeniti Boga ni tvoje dostojanstvo,

71
00:07:20,560 --> 00:07:22,160
[SPEAKER_00] da si dijete Boži.

72
00:07:22,160 --> 00:07:25,879
[SPEAKER_00] Nema u ljubavi sunca moja kompenzacije.

73
00:07:25,879 --> 00:07:28,060
[SPEAKER_00] Mnogi to rade.

74
00:07:28,060 --> 00:07:31,120
[SPEAKER_00] I zato sam rekao, jer ne poznaju sebe,

75
00:07:31,120 --> 00:07:33,180
[SPEAKER_00] svoj identitet,

76
00:07:33,180 --> 00:07:34,720
[SPEAKER_00] svoje

77
00:07:34,720 --> 00:07:36,399
[SPEAKER_00] slabosti,

78
00:07:36,399 --> 00:07:38,959
[SPEAKER_00] i onda kad im se dogodi nešto tako,

79
00:07:38,959 --> 00:07:41,899
[SPEAKER_00] ne samo da padne ljubav ili veza,

80
00:07:41,899 --> 00:07:43,180
[SPEAKER_00] nego padne

81
00:07:43,180 --> 00:07:44,759
[SPEAKER_00] cijeli sustav.

82
00:07:44,759 --> 00:07:47,040
[SPEAKER_00] Zato Isus

83
00:07:47,040 --> 00:07:48,860
[SPEAKER_00] čuje riječi od Boga.

84
00:07:48,860 --> 00:07:50,259
[SPEAKER_00] Ti si moj ljubljeni sin.

85
00:07:50,259 --> 00:07:52,800
[SPEAKER_00] To je ono što imi prije svega,

86
00:07:52,800 --> 00:07:54,759
[SPEAKER_00] da bi bili vi mladi,

87
00:07:54,759 --> 00:07:56,139
[SPEAKER_00] sposobni za ljubav,

88
00:07:56,139 --> 00:07:57,480
[SPEAKER_00] sposobni za brak,

89
00:07:57,480 --> 00:07:59,160
[SPEAKER_00] sposobni za jednu dobru vezu.

90
00:07:59,759 --> 00:08:03,360
[SPEAKER_00] Prvo morate biti vi svjesni svog identiteta,

91
00:08:03,360 --> 00:08:06,540
[SPEAKER_00] emocionalno i duhovno sanirani,

92
00:08:06,540 --> 00:08:07,639
[SPEAKER_00] ispravni,

93
00:08:07,639 --> 00:08:10,300
[SPEAKER_00] da ne bi bili ljubavni,

94
00:08:10,300 --> 00:08:14,040
[SPEAKER_00] emocionalni vampiri drugoj osobi.

95
00:08:14,779 --> 00:08:16,500
[SPEAKER_00] I to se često događa.

96
00:08:16,500 --> 00:08:18,160
[SPEAKER_00] Mnogi ljudi,

97
00:08:18,160 --> 00:08:20,139
[SPEAKER_00] kad izgube neku osobu ili vezu,

98
00:08:20,139 --> 00:08:23,500
[SPEAKER_00] znate koliko se meni na dnevnoj bazi ljudi javi,

99
00:08:23,500 --> 00:08:24,980
[SPEAKER_00] jučer mi je pukla veza,

100
00:08:24,980 --> 00:08:25,879
[SPEAKER_00] ili se rastajem,

101
00:08:25,879 --> 00:08:27,060
[SPEAKER_00] ili nešto šta da radim.

102
00:08:27,060 --> 00:08:28,839
[SPEAKER_00] Pa da ti jučer nije pukla veza,

103
00:08:28,839 --> 00:08:30,420
[SPEAKER_00] ti se ni danas Boga ne bi sjetio.

104
00:08:32,419 --> 00:08:34,139
[SPEAKER_00] Ajde, probajte se nek ste u vezama,

105
00:08:34,139 --> 00:08:35,259
[SPEAKER_00] nek ste u brakovima.

106
00:08:35,259 --> 00:08:38,080
[SPEAKER_00] Probajte se li bi tvoj život sad funkcionirao

107
00:08:38,080 --> 00:08:39,039
[SPEAKER_00] da te nema osobe.

108
00:08:39,039 --> 00:08:40,080
[SPEAKER_00] Kako bi se osjećao?

109
00:08:40,080 --> 00:08:41,379
[SPEAKER_00] Li bi mogo preživjeti?

110
00:08:41,379 --> 00:08:44,899
[SPEAKER_00] Ili je to kraj tvojeg svijeta?

111
00:08:44,899 --> 00:08:45,639
[SPEAKER_00] Gotovo je.

112
00:08:45,639 --> 00:08:46,700
[SPEAKER_00] Nemame više,

113
00:08:46,700 --> 00:08:47,600
[SPEAKER_00] sve je propalo,

114
00:08:47,600 --> 00:08:48,620
[SPEAKER_00] sve se raspalo.

115
00:08:48,620 --> 00:08:51,620
[SPEAKER_00] I to nam onda vrlo lako kaže

116
00:08:51,620 --> 00:08:53,679
[SPEAKER_00] što smo mi zapravo u životu

117
00:08:53,679 --> 00:08:55,840
[SPEAKER_00] uopće stavili na prvo mjesto.

118
00:08:55,840 --> 00:08:59,799
[SPEAKER_00] A kad mi ulazimo nezdreli,

119
00:09:00,480 --> 00:09:02,580
[SPEAKER_00] nesvjesni svog identiteta u veze.

120
00:09:02,580 --> 00:09:05,139
[SPEAKER_00] Što se mnogima događa?

121
00:09:05,139 --> 00:09:08,720
[SPEAKER_00] Veza postaje ovisnost.

122
00:09:08,720 --> 00:09:10,679
[SPEAKER_00] Svaka veza,

123
00:09:10,679 --> 00:09:12,399
[SPEAKER_00] ako je imala normalna,

124
00:09:12,399 --> 00:09:15,620
[SPEAKER_00] treba imati absolutnu slobodu i povjerenje.

125
00:09:15,620 --> 00:09:18,919
[SPEAKER_00] Ako si toliko ovisan u toj osobi

126
00:09:18,919 --> 00:09:20,179
[SPEAKER_00] da ne znaš ni svoj identitet,

127
00:09:20,179 --> 00:09:22,019
[SPEAKER_00] da ne znaš disat bez te osobe,

128
00:09:22,019 --> 00:09:24,779
[SPEAKER_00] Buras, ostavi se pitanje šta je s tobom.

129
00:09:24,779 --> 00:09:27,440
[SPEAKER_00] Koji ti je identitet?

130
00:09:28,379 --> 00:09:32,080
[SPEAKER_00] Ako si ti u vezi ovisan od toj osobi,

131
00:09:32,080 --> 00:09:34,820
[SPEAKER_00] jesi li od svog partnera ili partnerice

132
00:09:34,820 --> 00:09:36,659
[SPEAKER_00] napravio kumir ili zlatno tele

133
00:09:36,659 --> 00:09:37,480
[SPEAKER_00] ili drugog Boga

134
00:09:37,480 --> 00:09:41,419
[SPEAKER_00] da ti ne uspivaš funkcionirati bez te osobe?

135
00:09:41,419 --> 00:09:44,299
[SPEAKER_00] Znate, ljudi koji se ne mogu dva dana rastati

136
00:09:44,299 --> 00:09:45,879
[SPEAKER_00] na godišnjem ili poslovno,

137
00:09:45,879 --> 00:09:50,279
[SPEAKER_00] jer evo, odma je neki strah.

138
00:09:50,940 --> 00:09:54,279
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, nema ljubavi ukoliko smo ovisni.

139
00:09:54,279 --> 00:09:55,299
[SPEAKER_00] To nije sloboda.

140
00:09:55,299 --> 00:09:57,659
[SPEAKER_00] Drugo što se događa,

141
00:09:57,659 --> 00:10:01,120
[SPEAKER_00] kako je to ljubav u kojoj postaje strah?

142
00:10:01,120 --> 00:10:04,759
[SPEAKER_00] Strah da ćeš izgubiti tu osobu,

143
00:10:04,759 --> 00:10:06,860
[SPEAKER_00] da ne možeš funkcionirati bez nje.

144
00:10:08,460 --> 00:10:10,700
[SPEAKER_00] Kako je to ljubav u kojoj postoji strah?

145
00:10:10,700 --> 00:10:12,740
[SPEAKER_00] A to je ono što sam rekao,

146
00:10:12,740 --> 00:10:13,820
[SPEAKER_00] sve obrnutro.

147
00:10:13,820 --> 00:10:15,539
[SPEAKER_00] I što još najgore,

148
00:10:15,539 --> 00:10:18,279
[SPEAKER_00] kad si emocionalno

149
00:10:18,279 --> 00:10:20,539
[SPEAKER_00] i nezrel,

150
00:10:20,539 --> 00:10:22,679
[SPEAKER_00] kad nisi svjestan svog identiteta,

151
00:10:22,679 --> 00:10:25,519
[SPEAKER_00] drugi partner

152
00:10:25,519 --> 00:10:28,600
[SPEAKER_00] postaje sudac tvoje vrijednosti.

153
00:10:28,600 --> 00:10:33,480
[SPEAKER_00] To nije dobro.

154
00:10:33,480 --> 00:10:36,039
[SPEAKER_00] Jako je bitno

155
00:10:36,039 --> 00:10:37,700
[SPEAKER_00] da morate znati

156
00:10:37,700 --> 00:10:39,200
[SPEAKER_00] da vrijedite

157
00:10:39,200 --> 00:10:42,419
[SPEAKER_00] i bez neke veze.

158
00:10:42,419 --> 00:10:45,480
[SPEAKER_00] Nije samo ako ste traženi,

159
00:10:45,480 --> 00:10:47,539
[SPEAKER_00] nije samo ako ste primijećeni,

160
00:10:47,539 --> 00:10:49,659
[SPEAKER_00] nije samo ako ste u vezi

161
00:10:49,659 --> 00:10:51,179
[SPEAKER_00] da vrijedite.

162
00:10:51,179 --> 00:10:53,419
[SPEAKER_00] Mnogi morate znati,

163
00:10:53,419 --> 00:10:55,320
[SPEAKER_00] a doći ću do ovoga

164
00:10:55,320 --> 00:10:56,779
[SPEAKER_00] zašto dolazi do toga

165
00:10:56,779 --> 00:10:58,039
[SPEAKER_00] da se pojedini

166
00:10:58,039 --> 00:10:59,200
[SPEAKER_00] osjećaju

167
00:10:59,200 --> 00:11:01,519
[SPEAKER_00] sa 30, 25 godina

168
00:11:01,519 --> 00:11:03,679
[SPEAKER_00] već da ne vrijede.

169
00:11:03,679 --> 00:11:05,379
[SPEAKER_00] Ja se naježim

170
00:11:05,379 --> 00:11:06,519
[SPEAKER_00] kad čujem od mladih ljudi

171
00:11:06,519 --> 00:11:06,799
[SPEAKER_00] i kaže,

172
00:11:06,799 --> 00:11:07,659
[SPEAKER_00] moje je prošlo.

173
00:11:07,659 --> 00:11:09,600
[SPEAKER_00] Pa šta je prošlo sunce?

174
00:11:09,600 --> 00:11:10,899
[SPEAKER_00] Moje, tek si počeo živiti.

175
00:11:10,899 --> 00:11:12,940
[SPEAKER_00] Ali hoće reći

176
00:11:12,940 --> 00:11:14,019
[SPEAKER_00] u kontekstu ljubavi,

177
00:11:14,019 --> 00:11:15,379
[SPEAKER_00] veza i odnosa.

178
00:11:15,379 --> 00:11:16,980
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže, moje je prošlo.

179
00:11:16,980 --> 00:11:19,240
[SPEAKER_00] A onda s drugu stranu

180
00:11:19,240 --> 00:11:21,440
[SPEAKER_00] neka baka dođe na ispovjed

181
00:11:21,440 --> 00:11:21,840
[SPEAKER_00] pa kaže,

182
00:11:21,840 --> 00:11:22,840
[SPEAKER_00] imam ja prijatelja.

183
00:11:25,120 --> 00:11:27,639
[SPEAKER_00] vidite da nije prošlo sve.

184
00:11:27,639 --> 00:11:32,899
[SPEAKER_00] Jako je bitno da znaš,

185
00:11:32,899 --> 00:11:33,799
[SPEAKER_00] da vrijediš,

186
00:11:33,799 --> 00:11:36,559
[SPEAKER_00] jer jako je bitno da u vezi

187
00:11:36,559 --> 00:11:37,740
[SPEAKER_00] si slobodan,

188
00:11:37,740 --> 00:11:38,580
[SPEAKER_00] da možeš voljeti,

189
00:11:38,580 --> 00:11:40,960
[SPEAKER_00] da se ne moraš prodavati,

190
00:11:40,960 --> 00:11:43,279
[SPEAKER_00] da se ne moraš ničega bojati,

191
00:11:43,279 --> 00:11:45,159
[SPEAKER_00] da se ne budiš sa grčem.

192
00:11:48,700 --> 00:11:50,759
[SPEAKER_00] Vjerujem li da sam već ljubljen?

193
00:11:50,759 --> 00:11:52,159
[SPEAKER_00] To je ono pitanje

194
00:11:52,159 --> 00:11:53,799
[SPEAKER_00] koje si trebate postaviti.

195
00:11:53,799 --> 00:11:55,820
[SPEAKER_00] Ne da li će me neko ljubiti,

196
00:11:55,820 --> 00:11:58,860
[SPEAKER_00] da li će me neko primijetiti,

197
00:11:58,860 --> 00:12:00,299
[SPEAKER_00] nego da li vi

198
00:12:00,299 --> 00:12:02,480
[SPEAKER_00] osjećate u sebi duboko

199
00:12:02,480 --> 00:12:04,220
[SPEAKER_00] da si vrijedan

200
00:12:04,220 --> 00:12:05,720
[SPEAKER_00] i da te Bog ljubi

201
00:12:05,720 --> 00:12:06,700
[SPEAKER_00] tako kakav jesi,

202
00:12:06,700 --> 00:12:07,559
[SPEAKER_00] bez obzira

203
00:12:07,559 --> 00:12:09,360
[SPEAKER_00] je li imaš ti nekoga

204
00:12:09,360 --> 00:12:10,039
[SPEAKER_00] ili ne imaš.

205
00:12:10,039 --> 00:12:13,299
[SPEAKER_00] To je ključno pitanje.

206
00:12:13,299 --> 00:12:15,620
[SPEAKER_00] Kad si ti sretan i ljubljen

207
00:12:15,620 --> 00:12:17,080
[SPEAKER_00] i osjećaš to od Boga,

208
00:12:17,080 --> 00:12:20,559
[SPEAKER_00] ti si sposoban onda

209
00:12:20,559 --> 00:12:23,379
[SPEAKER_00] ući u neku vezu.

210
00:12:24,159 --> 00:12:24,960
[SPEAKER_00] Pogledajte ovo.

211
00:12:24,960 --> 00:12:28,000
[SPEAKER_00] Mi ste čuli danas u Evanđelju

212
00:12:28,000 --> 00:12:30,259
[SPEAKER_00] da su Isusa pritiskali,

213
00:12:30,259 --> 00:12:32,080
[SPEAKER_00] da se Isus pripremao

214
00:12:32,080 --> 00:12:33,320
[SPEAKER_00] pobjeće od mnoštva

215
00:12:33,320 --> 00:12:34,820
[SPEAKER_00] zato što su čuli

216
00:12:34,820 --> 00:12:35,960
[SPEAKER_00] da Isus radi čuda.

217
00:12:35,960 --> 00:12:37,820
[SPEAKER_00] I ovo mnoštvo

218
00:12:37,820 --> 00:12:39,019
[SPEAKER_00] ništa više u njemu

219
00:12:39,019 --> 00:12:39,639
[SPEAKER_00] nije vidjelo

220
00:12:39,639 --> 00:12:40,860
[SPEAKER_00] osim čudotvorca.

221
00:12:40,860 --> 00:12:43,019
[SPEAKER_00] I onda su se, kaže,

222
00:12:43,019 --> 00:12:44,000
[SPEAKER_00] bacali na njega.

223
00:12:44,000 --> 00:12:46,919
[SPEAKER_00] Doslovce da su ga gniečili već.

224
00:12:46,919 --> 00:12:48,779
[SPEAKER_00] I za njegovu,

225
00:12:48,779 --> 00:12:50,159
[SPEAKER_00] zbog opasnosti,

226
00:12:50,159 --> 00:12:51,899
[SPEAKER_00] morao je se popijeti na lađu

227
00:12:51,899 --> 00:12:53,840
[SPEAKER_00] da bi izmakao tom mnoštu.

228
00:12:54,159 --> 00:12:57,539
[SPEAKER_00] Koliko mi se bacamo na pod,

229
00:12:57,539 --> 00:12:58,659
[SPEAKER_00] molimo devetnice,

230
00:12:58,659 --> 00:12:59,960
[SPEAKER_00] daj muža, daj ženu,

231
00:12:59,960 --> 00:13:01,460
[SPEAKER_00] okreni ovu devetnicu,

232
00:13:01,460 --> 00:13:02,120
[SPEAKER_00] okreni onu,

233
00:13:02,120 --> 00:13:03,019
[SPEAKER_00] daj mi ovako,

234
00:13:03,019 --> 00:13:03,840
[SPEAKER_00] daj mi onako.

235
00:13:03,840 --> 00:13:06,240
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, mi smaramo Isusa.

236
00:13:06,240 --> 00:13:09,460
[SPEAKER_00] Doslovce, gniečimo ga.

237
00:13:09,460 --> 00:13:11,039
[SPEAKER_00] Evo vidite ovo mnoštvo.

238
00:13:11,039 --> 00:13:11,940
[SPEAKER_00] Pola vas je došlo

239
00:13:11,940 --> 00:13:13,139
[SPEAKER_00] samo zato što je tema ljubavi.

240
00:13:13,139 --> 00:13:14,320
[SPEAKER_00] Neće vas biti u korizmi,

241
00:13:14,320 --> 00:13:15,480
[SPEAKER_00] jer vas križ ne zanima.

242
00:13:15,480 --> 00:13:17,519
[SPEAKER_00] Vas srčeci zanimaju.

243
00:13:17,519 --> 00:13:24,120
[SPEAKER_00] I isto ovako mnoštvo,

244
00:13:24,159 --> 00:13:25,259
[SPEAKER_00] gniječilo Isusa.

245
00:13:25,259 --> 00:13:26,519
[SPEAKER_00] Bacalo se,

246
00:13:26,519 --> 00:13:27,600
[SPEAKER_00] daj mi ovo, daj mi ono.

247
00:13:27,600 --> 00:13:28,539
[SPEAKER_00] Ali što je problem?

248
00:13:28,539 --> 00:13:31,659
[SPEAKER_00] Što su gledali u Isusa čudotvorca.

249
00:13:31,659 --> 00:13:33,399
[SPEAKER_00] Drugim riječima,

250
00:13:33,399 --> 00:13:37,000
[SPEAKER_00] vlastite potrebe su i zaslijepile,

251
00:13:37,000 --> 00:13:39,639
[SPEAKER_00] zaslijepili da nisu prepoznali Isusa

252
00:13:39,639 --> 00:13:40,419
[SPEAKER_00] kao mesiju.

253
00:13:40,419 --> 00:13:43,620
[SPEAKER_00] Sunca mao ovo mnoštvo vas ovdje.

254
00:13:44,019 --> 00:13:46,059
[SPEAKER_00] Jesu i vas vlastite potrebe

255
00:13:46,059 --> 00:13:48,259
[SPEAKER_00] zaslijepile da se volko gurata u crkvu

256
00:13:48,259 --> 00:13:49,679
[SPEAKER_00] samo zato što je tema ljubavi?

257
00:13:49,679 --> 00:13:52,559
[SPEAKER_00] Jesu li i tvoje molitve svedene

258
00:13:52,559 --> 00:13:54,519
[SPEAKER_00] Isusu samo zbog tvojih potreba?

259
00:13:54,519 --> 00:13:57,539
[SPEAKER_00] Možda su i tebe tvoje potrebe

260
00:13:57,539 --> 00:13:59,179
[SPEAKER_00] zaslijepile pred Bogom,

261
00:13:59,179 --> 00:14:01,480
[SPEAKER_00] jer ga koristiš kao džuboks

262
00:14:01,480 --> 00:14:02,980
[SPEAKER_00] da ti ispuni želju,

263
00:14:02,980 --> 00:14:04,840
[SPEAKER_00] da ti pronađe muža, ženu, ljubav

264
00:14:04,840 --> 00:14:06,080
[SPEAKER_00] ili ne znam šta već tražiš

265
00:14:06,080 --> 00:14:07,259
[SPEAKER_00] za kuće mače, ne znam.

266
00:14:07,259 --> 00:14:09,460
[SPEAKER_00] Ali razumijete,

267
00:14:09,460 --> 00:14:13,440
[SPEAKER_00] nekada instrumentaliziramo Boga.

268
00:14:13,440 --> 00:14:15,200
[SPEAKER_00] Vlastite nas potrebe.

269
00:14:15,200 --> 00:14:17,259
[SPEAKER_00] Ja to vidim kod mladih ljudi.

270
00:14:17,259 --> 00:14:20,639
[SPEAKER_00] Čak neki dolaze do stupnja frustracije.

271
00:14:20,639 --> 00:14:22,759
[SPEAKER_00] Pa meni je 30, nemam nikoga.

272
00:14:22,759 --> 00:14:24,740
[SPEAKER_00] Meni se više ne da ni pokušavati.

273
00:14:24,740 --> 00:14:26,299
[SPEAKER_00] Ona je kaže, ja više ne vjerujem

274
00:14:26,299 --> 00:14:27,480
[SPEAKER_00] ni u ljubav da postoji.

275
00:14:27,480 --> 00:14:28,639
[SPEAKER_00] Ona je razočaran ovako,

276
00:14:28,639 --> 00:14:29,299
[SPEAKER_00] Ona je inako.

277
00:14:29,299 --> 00:14:33,179
[SPEAKER_00] I vidite, dolazimo do zaslijepiljenosti

278
00:14:33,179 --> 00:14:34,399
[SPEAKER_00] vlastitim potrebama.

279
00:14:34,840 --> 00:14:36,059
[SPEAKER_00] Mi ne tražimo Boga,

280
00:14:36,059 --> 00:14:38,500
[SPEAKER_00] već tražimo od Boga

281
00:14:38,500 --> 00:14:40,519
[SPEAKER_00] da nam to nešto ispuni.

282
00:14:40,519 --> 00:14:42,799
[SPEAKER_00] I zato dolazimo do očaja.

283
00:14:42,799 --> 00:14:45,840
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ako smo mi sjesni Bože ljubavi

284
00:14:45,840 --> 00:14:47,259
[SPEAKER_00] i svog identiteta,

285
00:14:47,259 --> 00:14:49,120
[SPEAKER_00] da ja vrijedim iako sam sam.

286
00:14:49,120 --> 00:14:52,019
[SPEAKER_00] Bože, ako si mi dao nekoga super,

287
00:14:52,019 --> 00:14:53,639
[SPEAKER_00] ako ga nema, opet super.

288
00:14:53,639 --> 00:14:56,159
[SPEAKER_00] I što se događa?

289
00:14:56,159 --> 00:14:57,580
[SPEAKER_00] Mnogi srljaju.

290
00:14:57,580 --> 00:15:00,860
[SPEAKER_00] Ali, kad ti sjesna svog identiteta

291
00:15:00,860 --> 00:15:02,519
[SPEAKER_00] i da si ljubljen od Boga,

292
00:15:03,299 --> 00:15:06,080
[SPEAKER_00] ti na vezu možeš čekat.

293
00:15:06,080 --> 00:15:08,019
[SPEAKER_00] Tebi se ne žuri toliko.

294
00:15:08,019 --> 00:15:10,279
[SPEAKER_00] Naravno da je fino da se udate

295
00:15:10,279 --> 00:15:11,440
[SPEAKER_00] i oženite svi na vrijeme.

296
00:15:11,440 --> 00:15:13,259
[SPEAKER_00] Ali,

297
00:15:13,259 --> 00:15:16,440
[SPEAKER_00] pa ne možeš upasti u krizu

298
00:15:16,440 --> 00:15:18,919
[SPEAKER_00] i frustraciju samo zato što imaš sad 30 godine

299
00:15:18,919 --> 00:15:19,860
[SPEAKER_00] i nisi našao nikoga

300
00:15:19,860 --> 00:15:21,080
[SPEAKER_00] i sad ćeš na ovo ruk nešto.

301
00:15:21,080 --> 00:15:22,940
[SPEAKER_00] Ne možeš učiniti ništa.

302
00:15:24,340 --> 00:15:25,440
[SPEAKER_00] Pa je si ti vrijedan života?

303
00:15:25,440 --> 00:15:26,679
[SPEAKER_00] Jesi.

304
00:15:26,679 --> 00:15:29,379
[SPEAKER_00] Jel imaš ti identiteta ako si sam?

305
00:15:29,379 --> 00:15:30,240
[SPEAKER_00] Imaš.

306
00:15:30,240 --> 00:15:33,779
[SPEAKER_00] Samo smo si mi umislili u glavi,

307
00:15:33,779 --> 00:15:35,200
[SPEAKER_00] ako ostanem sam,

308
00:15:35,200 --> 00:15:36,480
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam najjadniji.

309
00:15:36,480 --> 00:15:38,639
[SPEAKER_00] Naravno da Biblija preporuča

310
00:15:38,639 --> 00:15:40,200
[SPEAKER_00] da nije dobro da čovjek bude sam.

311
00:15:41,559 --> 00:15:42,980
[SPEAKER_00] Ali hoću reći

312
00:15:42,980 --> 00:15:45,220
[SPEAKER_00] kad si zrel

313
00:15:45,220 --> 00:15:46,759
[SPEAKER_00] za vezu,

314
00:15:46,759 --> 00:15:49,759
[SPEAKER_00] ti možeš čekat.

315
00:15:49,759 --> 00:15:52,259
[SPEAKER_00] Oni koji ne mogu čekat,

316
00:15:52,259 --> 00:15:53,139
[SPEAKER_00] koji srljaju.

317
00:15:53,139 --> 00:15:54,440
[SPEAKER_00] Pogledajte malo

318
00:15:54,440 --> 00:15:56,080
[SPEAKER_00] oni koji su imali duže veze.

319
00:15:56,080 --> 00:15:57,360
[SPEAKER_00] Čim prekine,

320
00:15:57,360 --> 00:15:58,879
[SPEAKER_00] ne može ni tjedan dana biti solo.

321
00:15:58,879 --> 00:16:00,159
[SPEAKER_00] Odmah u drugu vezu.

322
00:16:00,159 --> 00:16:00,460
[SPEAKER_00] Opa!

323
00:16:00,460 --> 00:16:03,019
[SPEAKER_00] Zače se nađe nešto?

324
00:16:03,019 --> 00:16:04,460
[SPEAKER_00] Primjeći.

325
00:16:04,460 --> 00:16:06,539
[SPEAKER_00] Ali je li to sreća?

326
00:16:06,539 --> 00:16:07,980
[SPEAKER_00] Ili je bijeg?

327
00:16:07,980 --> 00:16:10,220
[SPEAKER_00] Vi si dobro znate

328
00:16:10,220 --> 00:16:13,279
[SPEAKER_00] kad imate ozbiljniju ljubav i vezu,

329
00:16:13,279 --> 00:16:15,779
[SPEAKER_00] ipak smo mi emocionalna bića.

330
00:16:15,779 --> 00:16:17,980
[SPEAKER_00] Da se emocionalno saniraš,

331
00:16:17,980 --> 00:16:19,440
[SPEAKER_00] treba ti barem godina dana,

332
00:16:19,440 --> 00:16:20,559
[SPEAKER_00] a ne tjedan dana.

333
00:16:20,559 --> 00:16:22,659
[SPEAKER_00] I nikad mi nije bilo jasno

334
00:16:22,659 --> 00:16:24,379
[SPEAKER_00] kako neko može biti godinama u vezi,

335
00:16:24,379 --> 00:16:26,500
[SPEAKER_00] a za tjedan, dva ući u drugu.

336
00:16:26,500 --> 00:16:28,399
[SPEAKER_00] To znači

337
00:16:28,399 --> 00:16:30,720
[SPEAKER_00] da emocionalno nisi saniran.

338
00:16:30,720 --> 00:16:34,200
[SPEAKER_00] I od emocionalno nesaniranih ljudi bježite.

339
00:16:34,200 --> 00:16:37,679
[SPEAKER_00] Jer vam oni mogu dati samo bol i ogorčenost,

340
00:16:37,679 --> 00:16:38,379
[SPEAKER_00] ne ljubav.

341
00:16:39,779 --> 00:16:40,980
[SPEAKER_00] I zato vam govorim,

342
00:16:40,980 --> 00:16:42,700
[SPEAKER_00] nema žurbe.

343
00:16:42,700 --> 00:16:46,080
[SPEAKER_00] Kad si siguran u sebi i zadovoljan,

344
00:16:46,080 --> 00:16:47,539
[SPEAKER_00] nema očajavanja,

345
00:16:47,539 --> 00:16:50,159
[SPEAKER_00] jer mi je 25, 29, 30, 35.

346
00:16:50,159 --> 00:16:52,039
[SPEAKER_00] Nema očajavanja.

347
00:16:52,039 --> 00:16:53,720
[SPEAKER_00] Drugo,

348
00:16:55,840 --> 00:16:58,899
[SPEAKER_00] vas ljudi pola paralizira strah.

349
00:16:59,899 --> 00:17:03,220
[SPEAKER_00] Kad si svjestan svog identiteta i ljubavi Božije,

350
00:17:03,220 --> 00:17:06,000
[SPEAKER_00] možeš birati bez straha.

351
00:17:06,000 --> 00:17:11,420
[SPEAKER_00] Šta je to da toliki strahove imate upoznavati jedni druge?

352
00:17:12,519 --> 00:17:14,339
[SPEAKER_00] I tu bih mogo svašta iskomentirati.

353
00:17:14,339 --> 00:17:19,400
[SPEAKER_00] Ja jako vas potičem da se vi susrećujete,

354
00:17:19,400 --> 00:17:21,240
[SPEAKER_00] ali ne da pretjerujete.

355
00:17:22,940 --> 00:17:24,599
[SPEAKER_00] Nedavno sam s jednim mojim prijateljom.

356
00:17:24,599 --> 00:17:27,140
[SPEAKER_00] Rekao sam mu da će mi završiti u propovijed,

357
00:17:27,140 --> 00:17:28,680
[SPEAKER_00] jer mene dahnulo da ovo kažem,

358
00:17:28,680 --> 00:17:31,119
[SPEAKER_00] a možda i među vama mnogi tako radite.

359
00:17:33,660 --> 00:17:36,000
[SPEAKER_00] S jednim prijateljem pričao neki dan sam mu rekao

360
00:17:36,000 --> 00:17:37,140
[SPEAKER_00] da će završiti u propovijed,

361
00:17:37,140 --> 00:17:38,059
[SPEAKER_00] a tema je bila

362
00:17:38,059 --> 00:17:40,339
[SPEAKER_00] date.

363
00:17:40,339 --> 00:17:41,839
[SPEAKER_00] Odlazak na date.

364
00:17:41,839 --> 00:17:44,359
[SPEAKER_00] Ali to se nakupilo, brate,

365
00:17:44,359 --> 00:17:46,660
[SPEAKER_00] tri, četiri dejta u jednom tjednom.

366
00:17:46,660 --> 00:17:48,420
[SPEAKER_00] I onda ja kažem,

367
00:17:48,420 --> 00:17:49,200
[SPEAKER_00] a dobro, sokole,

368
00:17:49,200 --> 00:17:51,059
[SPEAKER_00] danas ćeš sa jednom,

369
00:17:51,059 --> 00:17:52,119
[SPEAKER_00] sutra s drugom,

370
00:17:52,119 --> 00:17:53,440
[SPEAKER_00] treći dan s trećom,

371
00:17:53,440 --> 00:17:55,519
[SPEAKER_00] i ti u petak opet ne znaš s kojom ćeš.

372
00:17:55,519 --> 00:17:59,279
[SPEAKER_00] A to je sasvim prirodno.

373
00:17:59,279 --> 00:17:59,740
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto?

374
00:17:59,740 --> 00:18:02,180
[SPEAKER_00] Pa kodobo ti se svidila frizura.

375
00:18:02,180 --> 00:18:03,619
[SPEAKER_00] Ona je bogata.

376
00:18:03,660 --> 00:18:05,079
[SPEAKER_00] ona je pametna.

377
00:18:05,079 --> 00:18:06,200
[SPEAKER_00] Ona je vakava.

378
00:18:06,200 --> 00:18:06,839
[SPEAKER_00] Ona je nakad.

379
00:18:06,839 --> 00:18:07,619
[SPEAKER_00] Ti se opet zbunjen.

380
00:18:07,619 --> 00:18:08,759
[SPEAKER_00] Ti opet sam ne znaš kojom bi.

381
00:18:08,759 --> 00:18:10,500
[SPEAKER_00] Kodobo ne ti se sviđa nešto,

382
00:18:10,500 --> 00:18:11,440
[SPEAKER_00] ali nije potpuno.

383
00:18:11,440 --> 00:18:13,720
[SPEAKER_00] E sad, kad bi se sve to moglo objedinti u jednu,

384
00:18:13,720 --> 00:18:15,099
[SPEAKER_00] to bi bila ta savršena.

385
00:18:15,099 --> 00:18:17,440
[SPEAKER_00] I šta vi radite?

386
00:18:17,440 --> 00:18:19,259
[SPEAKER_00] Vi zbunjujete sami sebe.

387
00:18:19,259 --> 00:18:22,220
[SPEAKER_00] Vi zbunjujete sami sebe.

388
00:18:22,220 --> 00:18:23,740
[SPEAKER_00] Jer zašto?

389
00:18:23,740 --> 00:18:26,140
[SPEAKER_00] Pa te se posvijeti jednu osobu.

390
00:18:26,140 --> 00:18:27,240
[SPEAKER_00] Ako ti se ne sviđa,

391
00:18:27,240 --> 00:18:28,559
[SPEAKER_00] onda lijepo raščistiš,

392
00:18:28,559 --> 00:18:30,059
[SPEAKER_00] pa ideš upoznavat drugu osobu.

393
00:18:30,059 --> 00:18:31,900
[SPEAKER_00] A ne,

394
00:18:33,640 --> 00:18:35,119
[SPEAKER_00] Mnogi voli biti, evo,

395
00:18:35,119 --> 00:18:37,220
[SPEAKER_00] biti primjećeni,

396
00:18:37,220 --> 00:18:38,700
[SPEAKER_00] o čemu i pričam cijelo vrijeme,

397
00:18:38,700 --> 00:18:40,140
[SPEAKER_00] da se nešto događa.

398
00:18:40,140 --> 00:18:41,799
[SPEAKER_00] Ali nije to dovoljno.

399
00:18:41,799 --> 00:18:43,160
[SPEAKER_00] To nije temelj dobar.

400
00:18:43,160 --> 00:18:44,599
[SPEAKER_00] Vi to dobro znate.

401
00:18:44,599 --> 00:18:46,799
[SPEAKER_00] I onda, ne možete tako,

402
00:18:46,799 --> 00:18:48,180
[SPEAKER_00] mislim, ne bi trebalo rati.

403
00:18:48,180 --> 00:18:52,720
[SPEAKER_00] I tu onda ne treba imati straha,

404
00:18:52,720 --> 00:18:54,759
[SPEAKER_00] ako si uopušten.

405
00:18:57,019 --> 00:18:59,019
[SPEAKER_00] Ono što još mnoge paralizira,

406
00:18:59,019 --> 00:19:02,680
[SPEAKER_00] je i strah da će u nekom odnosu,

407
00:19:02,680 --> 00:19:03,819
[SPEAKER_00] u nekoj vezi,

408
00:19:03,819 --> 00:19:04,940
[SPEAKER_00] izgubiti sebe.

409
00:19:04,940 --> 00:19:07,980
[SPEAKER_00] To mi je najkatastrofalnija stvar.

410
00:19:07,980 --> 00:19:10,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kako moši izgubiti sebe,

411
00:19:10,000 --> 00:19:11,059
[SPEAKER_00] ako poznaješ sebe?

412
00:19:11,059 --> 00:19:13,500
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, samo ako si nesiguran.

413
00:19:13,980 --> 00:19:15,200
[SPEAKER_00] To je, mi muškarci,

414
00:19:15,200 --> 00:19:17,220
[SPEAKER_00] mi to smijemo reći jedni drugim,

415
00:19:17,220 --> 00:19:18,680
[SPEAKER_00] ufacu zovemo papučarima.

416
00:19:18,680 --> 00:19:22,140
[SPEAKER_00] Znate, onaj koji nije siguran u sebi,

417
00:19:22,140 --> 00:19:23,259
[SPEAKER_00] čim nađe neku ribicu

418
00:19:23,259 --> 00:19:24,420
[SPEAKER_00] koja je malo oštirja ruka,

419
00:19:24,420 --> 00:19:26,579
[SPEAKER_00] on ne može ga prepoznaći oveće.

420
00:19:26,579 --> 00:19:27,819
[SPEAKER_00] On više i ne pije,

421
00:19:27,819 --> 00:19:28,660
[SPEAKER_00] on više ne izlazi,

422
00:19:28,660 --> 00:19:30,839
[SPEAKER_00] on ništa, svetac, preko noć.

423
00:19:30,839 --> 00:19:32,319
[SPEAKER_00] A on zapravo ne kuži

424
00:19:32,319 --> 00:19:33,220
[SPEAKER_00] da izgubi ove sebe.

425
00:19:33,220 --> 00:19:35,019
[SPEAKER_00] Razumijete?

426
00:19:35,019 --> 00:19:39,740
[SPEAKER_00] I mnogi imaju zato strah,

427
00:19:39,740 --> 00:19:41,240
[SPEAKER_00] ući u neki odnos

428
00:19:41,240 --> 00:19:42,279
[SPEAKER_00] da ne izgube sebe.

429
00:19:43,180 --> 00:19:44,160
[SPEAKER_00] I to je opravdano.

430
00:19:44,160 --> 00:19:45,700
[SPEAKER_00] Ne treba te biti niti

431
00:19:45,700 --> 00:19:46,839
[SPEAKER_00] u jednom odnosu,

432
00:19:46,839 --> 00:19:47,740
[SPEAKER_00] ni prijateljstvu,

433
00:19:47,740 --> 00:19:48,299
[SPEAKER_00] ni ljubavi,

434
00:19:48,299 --> 00:19:49,359
[SPEAKER_00] gdje ćeš izgubi sebe.

435
00:19:49,359 --> 00:19:50,420
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto?

436
00:19:50,420 --> 00:19:52,039
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto bi morao izgubi sebe?

437
00:19:52,039 --> 00:19:53,960
[SPEAKER_00] Ili te neko voli tako kakav jesi

438
00:19:53,960 --> 00:19:54,660
[SPEAKER_00] ili odkači?

439
00:19:54,660 --> 00:19:57,359
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, nemojte gubi sebe, ljudi.

440
00:19:57,359 --> 00:19:58,480
[SPEAKER_00] Jer zašto?

441
00:19:58,480 --> 00:19:59,819
[SPEAKER_00] Teško je se,

442
00:19:59,819 --> 00:20:01,039
[SPEAKER_00] nismo kamaleon,

443
00:20:01,039 --> 00:20:02,039
[SPEAKER_00] onaj, životinja.

444
00:20:02,039 --> 00:20:04,019
[SPEAKER_00] Ti možeš glumiti mjesec,

445
00:20:04,019 --> 00:20:05,160
[SPEAKER_00] dana, dva, u godini,

446
00:20:05,160 --> 00:20:06,640
[SPEAKER_00] dana u vezi,

447
00:20:06,640 --> 00:20:08,240
[SPEAKER_00] ali kad ta ćeš isplivat

448
00:20:08,240 --> 00:20:09,259
[SPEAKER_00] na površinu ti,

449
00:20:10,180 --> 00:20:11,599
[SPEAKER_00] ti koji jesi kakav jesi,

450
00:20:11,599 --> 00:20:14,140
[SPEAKER_00] onda bolje pokaži sve svoje

451
00:20:14,140 --> 00:20:15,380
[SPEAKER_00] najgore strane,

452
00:20:15,380 --> 00:20:16,779
[SPEAKER_00] odma pa ako te prihvati,

453
00:20:16,779 --> 00:20:17,319
[SPEAKER_00] prihvati,

454
00:20:17,319 --> 00:20:19,220
[SPEAKER_00] nego da te skuži

455
00:20:19,220 --> 00:20:20,039
[SPEAKER_00] za godinu dvije.

456
00:20:20,039 --> 00:20:22,119
[SPEAKER_00] E sad,

457
00:20:25,640 --> 00:20:27,400
[SPEAKER_00] ona rečenica s kojoj bi svi trebali

458
00:20:27,400 --> 00:20:28,319
[SPEAKER_00] odavde ići,

459
00:20:28,319 --> 00:20:29,859
[SPEAKER_00] a to je s mišlju,

460
00:20:29,859 --> 00:20:32,160
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam vrijedan i ljubljen od Boga,

461
00:20:32,160 --> 00:20:33,779
[SPEAKER_00] bez obzira jesam li sam,

462
00:20:33,779 --> 00:20:34,660
[SPEAKER_00] imam li koga,

463
00:20:34,660 --> 00:20:35,579
[SPEAKER_00] ili bilo što.

464
00:20:35,579 --> 00:20:36,960
[SPEAKER_00] Međutim,

465
00:20:36,960 --> 00:20:38,480
[SPEAKER_00] uvijek se tu nama negdje,

466
00:20:38,480 --> 00:20:40,180
[SPEAKER_00] iza ove rečenice,

467
00:20:40,180 --> 00:20:43,039
[SPEAKER_00] da li me neko voli

468
00:20:43,039 --> 00:20:44,819
[SPEAKER_00] i da li sam vrijedan ljubavi,

469
00:20:44,819 --> 00:20:46,779
[SPEAKER_00] ipak moram reći,

470
00:20:46,779 --> 00:20:48,680
[SPEAKER_00] kriju neke rane.

471
00:20:48,680 --> 00:20:51,039
[SPEAKER_00] Nije ta rečenica,

472
00:20:51,039 --> 00:20:52,359
[SPEAKER_00] kad neko kaže tako,

473
00:20:52,359 --> 00:20:53,279
[SPEAKER_00] samo bez vezi.

474
00:20:54,480 --> 00:20:56,279
[SPEAKER_00] Možda to nisu neke velike rane,

475
00:20:56,279 --> 00:20:57,039
[SPEAKER_00] koje krvare,

476
00:20:57,039 --> 00:20:57,900
[SPEAKER_00] koje mi vidimo,

477
00:20:57,900 --> 00:21:00,380
[SPEAKER_00] ali su to možda neki trenuci,

478
00:21:00,380 --> 00:21:03,359
[SPEAKER_00] kad baš nismo bili primijećeni,

479
00:21:03,359 --> 00:21:05,660
[SPEAKER_00] ili kad nismo bili pohvaljeni,

480
00:21:05,660 --> 00:21:09,700
[SPEAKER_00] ili kad nismo bili natopljeni

481
00:21:09,700 --> 00:21:11,779
[SPEAKER_00] nekom pažnom, ljubavljom, empatijom,

482
00:21:11,779 --> 00:21:13,059
[SPEAKER_00] koji su nas možda ranile.

483
00:21:13,059 --> 00:21:15,880
[SPEAKER_00] Kažem, nisu to najčešće rane neke velike,

484
00:21:15,880 --> 00:21:17,880
[SPEAKER_00] koje su nas ubile i krvare trenutno.

485
00:21:17,880 --> 00:21:19,480
[SPEAKER_00] Ali sve te sitnice,

486
00:21:19,480 --> 00:21:20,819
[SPEAKER_00] trenuci odbacivanja,

487
00:21:20,819 --> 00:21:21,940
[SPEAKER_00] neprimjećivanja,

488
00:21:21,940 --> 00:21:23,240
[SPEAKER_00] nesigurnosti,

489
00:21:23,339 --> 00:21:25,700
[SPEAKER_00] strahova su oblikovale naše srce.

490
00:21:25,700 --> 00:21:28,599
[SPEAKER_00] I to negdje u nama tu čuči.

491
00:21:28,599 --> 00:21:30,940
[SPEAKER_00] Kakvu sliku imamo o sebi?

492
00:21:35,019 --> 00:21:37,500
[SPEAKER_00] Nažalost, puno puta

493
00:21:37,500 --> 00:21:40,619
[SPEAKER_00] kažemo i čujemo,

494
00:21:40,619 --> 00:21:43,299
[SPEAKER_00] kad iz nas rane progovaraju,

495
00:21:43,299 --> 00:21:44,980
[SPEAKER_00] čujemo tu rečenicu,

496
00:21:44,980 --> 00:21:46,900
[SPEAKER_00] neće me nikog tjeti.

497
00:21:46,900 --> 00:21:49,099
[SPEAKER_00] Ako me neko upozna,

498
00:21:49,099 --> 00:21:50,220
[SPEAKER_00] i otići će od mene.

499
00:21:50,220 --> 00:21:51,960
[SPEAKER_00] Bolje je loša veza,

500
00:21:51,960 --> 00:21:53,059
[SPEAKER_00] nego biti sam.

501
00:21:53,859 --> 00:21:55,440
[SPEAKER_00] Imate i tih kompromisa,

502
00:21:55,440 --> 00:21:56,059
[SPEAKER_00] nažalost.

503
00:21:56,059 --> 00:21:57,920
[SPEAKER_00] Ali tu treba

504
00:21:57,920 --> 00:21:59,900
[SPEAKER_00] doći Isusu.

505
00:21:59,900 --> 00:22:03,720
[SPEAKER_00] Ljubav je često

506
00:22:03,720 --> 00:22:05,799
[SPEAKER_00] područje ranljivo.

507
00:22:05,799 --> 00:22:08,519
[SPEAKER_00] I nema ko nije na tom području

508
00:22:08,519 --> 00:22:09,500
[SPEAKER_00] nekada bio ranjen.

509
00:22:09,500 --> 00:22:12,240
[SPEAKER_00] I sad ne znam jeste to izcijeli,

510
00:22:12,240 --> 00:22:12,799
[SPEAKER_00] li niste,

511
00:22:13,400 --> 00:22:14,740
[SPEAKER_00] ali najgora je stvar

512
00:22:14,740 --> 00:22:16,400
[SPEAKER_00] da ono što vam je bilo

513
00:22:16,400 --> 00:22:17,720
[SPEAKER_00] negdje u nekom odnosu

514
00:22:17,720 --> 00:22:19,460
[SPEAKER_00] prenosite u drugi odnos.

515
00:22:19,460 --> 00:22:21,740
[SPEAKER_00] Zato je važno

516
00:22:21,740 --> 00:22:23,339
[SPEAKER_00] izliječiti i zacijeliti.

517
00:22:23,339 --> 00:22:26,599
[SPEAKER_00] Isus kad nas liječi,

518
00:22:26,599 --> 00:22:27,400
[SPEAKER_00] on ne govori

519
00:22:27,400 --> 00:22:28,420
[SPEAKER_00] kao što mi prijatelji

520
00:22:28,420 --> 00:22:29,440
[SPEAKER_00] jedni druge tješimo.

521
00:22:29,440 --> 00:22:30,359
[SPEAKER_00] Daj, možeš ti,

522
00:22:30,359 --> 00:22:31,079
[SPEAKER_00] budi jaka,

523
00:22:31,079 --> 00:22:32,160
[SPEAKER_00] budi jak i zdrži,

524
00:22:32,160 --> 00:22:33,180
[SPEAKER_00] ma imaj bolji od te,

525
00:22:33,180 --> 00:22:33,619
[SPEAKER_00] šta ti,

526
00:22:33,619 --> 00:22:34,500
[SPEAKER_00] ajde popij jedno,

527
00:22:34,500 --> 00:22:35,299
[SPEAKER_00] proći će to.

528
00:22:35,299 --> 00:22:38,240
[SPEAKER_00] Isus nije tješi tako.

529
00:22:38,240 --> 00:22:41,200
[SPEAKER_00] Isus je prvi prošao

530
00:22:41,200 --> 00:22:41,980
[SPEAKER_00] odbačenost.

531
00:22:42,759 --> 00:22:44,440
[SPEAKER_00] Isus je prvi bio izdan.

532
00:22:44,440 --> 00:22:46,420
[SPEAKER_00] Isus kad je visio na križu

533
00:22:46,420 --> 00:22:47,079
[SPEAKER_00] nije rekao,

534
00:22:47,079 --> 00:22:48,759
[SPEAKER_00] Bože, zašto boli me,

535
00:22:48,759 --> 00:22:49,980
[SPEAKER_00] zašto ja moram patiti.

536
00:22:49,980 --> 00:22:54,359
[SPEAKER_00] Nas kad zadesi bol od ljubavi,

537
00:22:54,359 --> 00:22:55,619
[SPEAKER_00] onda smo šokirani,

538
00:22:55,619 --> 00:22:57,640
[SPEAKER_00] paralizirani.

539
00:22:57,640 --> 00:22:59,599
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto mi se ovo dogodilo?

540
00:22:59,599 --> 00:23:00,900
[SPEAKER_00] Šta ću sad?

541
00:23:00,900 --> 00:23:02,019
[SPEAKER_00] Međutim,

542
00:23:02,019 --> 00:23:03,680
[SPEAKER_00] Isus ne ohrabruje

543
00:23:03,680 --> 00:23:04,980
[SPEAKER_00] kao što mi ohrabrujemo.

544
00:23:04,980 --> 00:23:07,359
[SPEAKER_00] Isus ulazi u našu bol,

545
00:23:07,359 --> 00:23:10,240
[SPEAKER_00] imenuje je

546
00:23:10,240 --> 00:23:11,819
[SPEAKER_00] i dotiče je.

547
00:23:12,119 --> 00:23:14,720
[SPEAKER_00] i uvodite u istinu.

548
00:23:14,720 --> 00:23:16,680
[SPEAKER_00] I to je najbitnije.

549
00:23:16,680 --> 00:23:18,359
[SPEAKER_00] Jer samo je to proces

550
00:23:18,359 --> 00:23:20,059
[SPEAKER_00] kako ćeš osraditi.

551
00:23:20,059 --> 00:23:21,799
[SPEAKER_00] A što je istina?

552
00:23:21,799 --> 00:23:24,000
[SPEAKER_00] Istina nije.

553
00:23:24,000 --> 00:23:26,920
[SPEAKER_00] Nitko me nije htio.

554
00:23:26,920 --> 00:23:28,599
[SPEAKER_00] Istina je,

555
00:23:28,599 --> 00:23:32,019
[SPEAKER_00] nekime ljudi nisu znali boljeti.

556
00:23:32,019 --> 00:23:34,319
[SPEAKER_00] Vidite kako dvije rečence

557
00:23:34,319 --> 00:23:35,700
[SPEAKER_00] različito zvuče.

558
00:23:36,779 --> 00:23:38,099
[SPEAKER_00] pa i kad te neko ranio,

559
00:23:38,099 --> 00:23:40,039
[SPEAKER_00] nije znao cijeniti tvoju ljubav.

560
00:23:40,519 --> 00:23:41,400
[SPEAKER_00] nemoj reći,

561
00:23:41,400 --> 00:23:43,440
[SPEAKER_00] nemoj se tako ponašati,

562
00:23:43,440 --> 00:23:45,680
[SPEAKER_00] nemoj nikada reći,

563
00:23:45,680 --> 00:23:47,059
[SPEAKER_00] niko me nije htijeo

564
00:23:47,059 --> 00:23:48,359
[SPEAKER_00] ili me ostavio,

565
00:23:48,359 --> 00:23:49,960
[SPEAKER_00] nego samo lijepo reci,

566
00:23:49,960 --> 00:23:52,519
[SPEAKER_00] nekime ljudi nisu znali voljeti.

567
00:23:52,519 --> 00:23:54,480
[SPEAKER_00] To je velika razlika.

568
00:23:54,480 --> 00:23:55,559
[SPEAKER_00] E to je istina.

569
00:23:57,619 --> 00:23:59,019
[SPEAKER_00] Drugi nas nekad uvjere

570
00:23:59,019 --> 00:24:00,019
[SPEAKER_00] da smo smotani,

571
00:24:00,019 --> 00:24:01,500
[SPEAKER_00] da smo bezvijedni,

572
00:24:01,500 --> 00:24:02,920
[SPEAKER_00] da ne znamo cijeniti ljubav.

573
00:24:02,920 --> 00:24:04,640
[SPEAKER_00] Ali to nije istina.

574
00:24:04,640 --> 00:24:05,480
[SPEAKER_00] Većina ljudi

575
00:24:05,480 --> 00:24:07,019
[SPEAKER_00] prihvaća ljubav

576
00:24:07,019 --> 00:24:08,500
[SPEAKER_00] jer im je potrebna.

577
00:24:08,500 --> 00:24:09,680
[SPEAKER_00] Međutim,

578
00:24:09,680 --> 00:24:11,940
[SPEAKER_00] ima i teške situacije

579
00:24:11,940 --> 00:24:13,299
[SPEAKER_00] gdje se ljubavi ne ostvavi.

580
00:24:13,299 --> 00:24:14,859
[SPEAKER_00] A nemoj krivi sebe,

581
00:24:14,859 --> 00:24:16,140
[SPEAKER_00] nego samo reci,

582
00:24:16,140 --> 00:24:17,880
[SPEAKER_00] ima ljudi koji nisu

583
00:24:17,880 --> 00:24:20,099
[SPEAKER_00] znali voljeti,

584
00:24:20,099 --> 00:24:21,680
[SPEAKER_00] koji me nisu znali voljeti.

585
00:24:21,680 --> 00:24:23,019
[SPEAKER_00] A nemoj govoriti

586
00:24:23,019 --> 00:24:24,680
[SPEAKER_00] nikome nije htio.

587
00:24:24,680 --> 00:24:27,240
[SPEAKER_00] Zato vas potičem

588
00:24:27,240 --> 00:24:30,740
[SPEAKER_00] ono što je Isus čuo

589
00:24:30,740 --> 00:24:33,539
[SPEAKER_00] da sebi često ponavljate u srcu.

590
00:24:33,539 --> 00:24:37,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja, moj identitet je od Boga.

591
00:24:37,000 --> 00:24:39,480
[SPEAKER_00] Mene Bog voli vako kakav je sam.

592
00:24:39,480 --> 00:24:41,579
[SPEAKER_00] Bogu sam zahvalan

593
00:24:41,579 --> 00:24:42,640
[SPEAKER_00] ako sam blagoslovljen

594
00:24:42,640 --> 00:24:43,519
[SPEAKER_00] da imam nekoga.

595
00:24:43,519 --> 00:24:45,380
[SPEAKER_00] Ako trenutno ne imam nekoga,

596
00:24:45,380 --> 00:24:46,480
[SPEAKER_00] poslaću mi.

597
00:24:46,480 --> 00:24:47,819
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam u Božim rukama.

598
00:24:47,819 --> 00:24:49,859
[SPEAKER_00] Nemojte pritiskati Isusa

599
00:24:49,859 --> 00:24:51,819
[SPEAKER_00] gniečiti kovi danas u Evanđelju.

600
00:24:51,819 --> 00:24:53,539
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto?

601
00:24:53,539 --> 00:24:55,660
[SPEAKER_00] Zato što Isusa treba slušati.

602
00:24:56,859 --> 00:24:58,480
[SPEAKER_00] Isus nije tu za nas

603
00:24:58,480 --> 00:25:00,359
[SPEAKER_00] da ostvaruje

604
00:25:00,359 --> 00:25:02,299
[SPEAKER_00] one želje koje mene

605
00:25:02,299 --> 00:25:03,480
[SPEAKER_00] i tebe zasljepljuju.

606
00:25:03,480 --> 00:25:05,500
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam to više puta rekao.

607
00:25:05,500 --> 00:25:07,519
[SPEAKER_00] Dobro je da Bog ne uslišava

608
00:25:07,519 --> 00:25:08,420
[SPEAKER_00] sve naše želje.

609
00:25:09,700 --> 00:25:11,259
[SPEAKER_00] jer nisu uvijek sve dobre.

610
00:25:11,259 --> 00:25:13,759
[SPEAKER_00] Mi smo možda uvjereni

611
00:25:13,759 --> 00:25:14,700
[SPEAKER_00] u datom trenutku.

612
00:25:15,140 --> 00:25:17,720
[SPEAKER_00] ali tako nisu ni sve osobe za nas.

613
00:25:18,759 --> 00:25:20,700
[SPEAKER_00] vjerujem da ste puno puta

614
00:25:20,700 --> 00:25:22,539
[SPEAKER_00] mislili, pa čak možda i prvu ljubav

615
00:25:22,539 --> 00:25:23,559
[SPEAKER_00] koju ste u životu imali.

616
00:25:23,559 --> 00:25:24,140
[SPEAKER_00] To je to.

617
00:25:24,140 --> 00:25:25,059
[SPEAKER_00] To je ta.

618
00:25:25,059 --> 00:25:27,140
[SPEAKER_00] S tom ću završiti do kraja života.

619
00:25:27,140 --> 00:25:28,240
[SPEAKER_00] Pa ništa.

620
00:25:28,240 --> 00:25:31,220
[SPEAKER_00] Puno puta je to tako.

621
00:25:31,720 --> 00:25:34,380
[SPEAKER_00] ali ne treba se obeshrabriti.

622
00:25:34,380 --> 00:25:35,599
[SPEAKER_00] Jer vi,

623
00:25:35,599 --> 00:25:38,220
[SPEAKER_00] dok niste u sebi sigurni

624
00:25:38,220 --> 00:25:40,579
[SPEAKER_00] i jaki u sebi,

625
00:25:40,579 --> 00:25:44,279
[SPEAKER_00] nećete pronaći mir u vezi.

626
00:25:45,059 --> 00:25:46,579
[SPEAKER_00] I zato je to stalno nekada

627
00:25:46,579 --> 00:25:47,920
[SPEAKER_00] kada su dvije osobe,

628
00:25:47,920 --> 00:25:48,619
[SPEAKER_00] pogotovo

629
00:25:48,619 --> 00:25:51,759
[SPEAKER_00] ako je barem jedna nezrela,

630
00:25:51,759 --> 00:25:53,220
[SPEAKER_00] ali još gore ako su oba dvije,

631
00:25:53,220 --> 00:25:55,480
[SPEAKER_00] onda je tu opći kaos.

632
00:25:55,480 --> 00:25:56,839
[SPEAKER_00] To nekako se gura,

633
00:25:56,839 --> 00:25:58,680
[SPEAKER_00] ali je to uvijek stalno napita.

634
00:25:58,680 --> 00:26:00,559
[SPEAKER_00] Malo promislite

635
00:26:00,559 --> 00:26:02,579
[SPEAKER_00] vi koji ste uvezamili u braku.

636
00:26:02,579 --> 00:26:03,839
[SPEAKER_00] Jeste opušteni.

637
00:26:03,839 --> 00:26:05,119
[SPEAKER_00] Je vam lijepo.

638
00:26:05,119 --> 00:26:06,839
[SPEAKER_00] Jeste bez straha.

639
00:26:06,839 --> 00:26:09,480
[SPEAKER_00] To je ljubav.

640
00:26:09,480 --> 00:26:10,759
[SPEAKER_00] Znate,

641
00:26:10,759 --> 00:26:13,539
[SPEAKER_00] ovdje ove cure u zboru

642
00:26:13,539 --> 00:26:14,380
[SPEAKER_00] imaju violinu.

643
00:26:15,059 --> 00:26:17,559
[SPEAKER_00] Ja ne razumijem se ništa o glazbi,

644
00:26:17,559 --> 00:26:18,740
[SPEAKER_00] ali ovako promatram.

645
00:26:18,740 --> 00:26:21,579
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, nekad su naši odnosi

646
00:26:21,579 --> 00:26:23,019
[SPEAKER_00] poput instrumentata.

647
00:26:23,019 --> 00:26:26,019
[SPEAKER_00] Morate točno pogoditi

648
00:26:26,019 --> 00:26:28,160
[SPEAKER_00] jačinu.

649
00:26:28,160 --> 00:26:31,480
[SPEAKER_00] Ako je nešto slabo,

650
00:26:31,480 --> 00:26:32,480
[SPEAKER_00] opet se ne čuje.

651
00:26:32,480 --> 00:26:35,180
[SPEAKER_00] Ali opet vjerujem da one žice,

652
00:26:35,180 --> 00:26:37,180
[SPEAKER_00] ako prenategneš gore onaj ključ

653
00:26:37,180 --> 00:26:38,619
[SPEAKER_00] što se navija ili gitaru,

654
00:26:38,619 --> 00:26:40,079
[SPEAKER_00] one će popucati.

655
00:26:40,079 --> 00:26:42,720
[SPEAKER_00] Mora se pronaći sredina.

656
00:26:43,539 --> 00:26:45,119
[SPEAKER_00] Naši odnosi nekada,

657
00:26:45,119 --> 00:26:46,920
[SPEAKER_00] obiteljski,

658
00:26:46,920 --> 00:26:48,220
[SPEAKER_00] brakovi,

659
00:26:48,220 --> 00:26:49,079
[SPEAKER_00] veze,

660
00:26:49,079 --> 00:26:50,160
[SPEAKER_00] prijateljstva,

661
00:26:50,160 --> 00:26:52,059
[SPEAKER_00] su pre nategnuti.

662
00:26:52,059 --> 00:26:54,000
[SPEAKER_00] Dovoljno je jedna riječ

663
00:26:54,000 --> 00:26:55,279
[SPEAKER_00] i žice pucaju.

664
00:26:55,279 --> 00:26:56,000
[SPEAKER_00] Amen.

